Class RList<E>

java.lang.Object
  react.Reactor<RList.Listener<E>>
      react.RList<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, List<E>
public class RList<E>
extends Reactor<RList.Listener<E>>
implements List<E>

Provides a reactive model of a list. Note that remove(java.lang.Object) will not trigger a notification if the removed element is not present in the list. Use removeForce(E) to force a notification.
